== 制作 ==
2008年导演史蒂夫·麦奎因对编剧[[約翰·瑞雷|約翰·瑞雷]]表示，自己有兴趣拍摄一部美国[[奴隶制|奴隶制]]题材的电影<ref>{{cite web|last=Thompson|first=Anne|title=John Ridley Talks Writing '12 Years a Slave' and Directing Hendrix Biopic 'All Is by My Side'|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/john-ridley-talks-writing-12-years-a-slave-and-directing-hendrix-biopic-all-is-by-my-side|work=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|publisher={{tsl|en|Snagfilms||Snagfilms}}|accessdate=2013-10-25|date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013203658/http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/john-ridley-talks-writing-12-years-a-slave-and-directing-hendrix-biopic-all-is-by-my-side|archive-date=2013-10-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。后来麦奎因的合作伙伴 Bianca Stigter 将所罗门所著的书籍推荐给了麦奎因，麦奎因读完后被书中故事深深震动，认为它与[[二战|二战]]期间由少女[[安妮·弗兰克|安妮·弗兰克]]所写的《[[安妮日记|安妮日记]]》一样有重要的历史价值，决定将其改拍成电影<ref>{{cite web|title='12 Years A Slave' Was A Film That 'No One Was Making'|url=http://www.npr.org/2013/10/24/240288057/12-years-a-slave-was-a-film-that-no-one-was-making|publisher=[[全国公共广播电台|NPR]]|accessdate=2013-10-25|date=2013-10-24|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213233642/https://www.npr.org/2013/10/24/240288057/12-years-a-slave-was-a-film-that-no-one-was-making|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此后得到 Plan B 等影视公司的支持。2011年8月，麦奎因宣布确定开拍本片，并由英国非裔演员[[切瓦特·埃加福特|切瓦特·埃加福特]]担纲主演<ref name="truitt"/><ref>{{cite journal | last=Sneider | first=Jeff | title=McQueen tallying '12 Years' at Plan B | journal=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | date=2011-08-17 }}</ref>。

